"{\"uid\": \"theinertia.com-surf-pablo-jimenez-shooting-from-water-olympic-surfing-events-most-epic-day\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Pablo was there for one of the most epic waves of Medina's career.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 66, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 50, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.914450265791664e-28, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pablo\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"the most epic waves\", \"from\": 27, \"to\": 46}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Photo:Pablo Jimenez//ISA When the first rays of light poked over the mountains of Tahiti on Monday, July 29,no one was expecting what the sun revealed.\", \"from\": 67, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 150, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.897467696433673e-13, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Photo\", \"from\": 67, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"Pablo Jimenez//ISA\", \"from\": 73, \"to\": 91}, {\"ngram\": \"the first rays\", \"from\": 97, \"to\": 111}, {\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 115, \"to\": 120}, {\"ngram\": \"the mountains\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 145}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 165}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 171}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 181}, {\"ngram\": \"the sun\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teahupo'o was huge and perfect with slabs of water exploding on the reef.\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"slabs\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 261}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By now you have probably seen the photos and videos of the Olympians who braved the conditions - heroic barrels, pounding wipeouts, and lagoon wash-throughs.\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the photos\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympians\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"the conditions - heroic barrels\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 405}, {\"ngram\": \"pounding wipeouts\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"lagoon wash-throughs\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there were also two water photographers putting themselves in the chaos, albeit without the flotation of a surfboard.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two water photographers\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 495}, {\"ngram\": \"the chaos\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"the flotation\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"a surfboard\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only two photographers had permission to shoot in the water at the Olympics at once.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only two photographers\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One was the AFP photographer, Ben Thouard, and the other was a rotating position between three ISA photographers.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999894143913, \"rank\": 9.182774426494055e-09, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rotating position\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"three ISA photographers\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On that special Monday, it wasPablo Jimenez'sturn.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that special Monday\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the swell coming from an extremely west direction, the lineup was particularly dangerous as the biggest sets threatened to close out the channel.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the swell\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"an extremely west direction\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"the lineup\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest sets\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"the channel\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given the moment and the conditions, it was a career-defining day for a photographer.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"the conditions\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"a career-defining day\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"a photographer\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I sat down with Jimenez, who's originally from Chile, to hear what it was like shooting in the water with just one other photographer and two surfers on that memorable morning.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9999999297697311, \"rank\": 6.999126255637881e-08, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jimenez\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"just one other photographer\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"two surfers\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"that memorable morning\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How was your experience that big Monday, especially in the context of the Olympics?\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your experience\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"the context\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Monday was fun.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1340, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We showed up that day knowing there would be a bit more swell than the previous two or three days.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that day\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous two or three days\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I was stoked when I saw the sets coming.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sets\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody expected it to be that big.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got in the water and the first heat was good, but then it really started pumping.\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"the first heat\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were some bombs out there.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some bombs\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How close could you get to the waves?\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I came here a couple of times before the Olympics for training camps.\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"training camps\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a really good spot to shoot either from water or the boat.\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really good spot\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's super photogenic.\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's a little shifty.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little shifty\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not know it was like that.\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They call it the south peak and the west bowl.\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1939, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the south peak\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"the west bowl\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It moves a little bit with swell directions.\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swell directions\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes you are really close to the action and sometimes it's further up the point.\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I still have not figured it out 100 percent.\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some guys get super close.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some guys\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wish I could get that close but I think you need to spend more time on it, get the feel, and just know the wave properly.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more time\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"the feel\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Would you have gotten closer to the surfers if it were a freesurf?\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the surfers\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"a freesurf\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, you always want to be closer, but there are local photographers and they have spent a fair amount of time out there.\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"local photographers\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2405}, {\"ngram\": \"a fair amount\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lineup for photographers is similar to a lineup for surfers.\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lineup\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\": \"photographers\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"a lineup\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2510}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I would not have necessarily been closer.\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was the good thing that day.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the good thing\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was just me and one other photographer.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one other photographer\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"None of my photos have another photographer in front, which is awesome.\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2717, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"None\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"my photos\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2663}, {\"ngram\": \"another photographer\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless of how close you were, was it sketchy with all that water moving around?\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all that water\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That day was so west.\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That day\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were a few sets that were almost closeouts.\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few sets\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"almost closeouts\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were coming from the direction where all the boats were sitting.\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the direction\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2911}, {\"ngram\": \"all the boats\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was this one set, I think it was right around the time Filipe Toledo got caught inside, that was super west.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 3060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3007, \"end\": 3020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipe_Toledo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Filipe Toledo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipe_Toledo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipe_Toledo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this one set\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"super west\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a bit chaotic at the time.\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was going under the set wave and then I looked up and saw the broadcast boat right there at the top of the wave - maybe six to eight feet away - the distances are a bit (hard to gauge) underwater.\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the set wave\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3125}, {\"ngram\": \"the broadcast boat\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3173}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3196}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3208}, {\"ngram\": \"the distances\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3255}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3265}, {\"ngram\": \"underwater\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I went under, opened my eyes, and saw the boat's propeller.\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my eyes\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3325}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat's propeller\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a little bit too close for comfort.\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"comfort\", \"from\": 3391, \"to\": 3398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wait, do you always open your eyes when going under?\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your eyes\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, I want to know where I am going.\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ok, continue.\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 3508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So (at that point) I stopped paddling and I started feeling the suction and the energy of the wave sucking me back.\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3527}, {\"ngram\": \"the suction\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3581}, {\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 3586, \"to\": 3596}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I changed my direction a bit and went around the boat.\", \"from\": 3626, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my direction\", \"from\": 3636, \"to\": 3648}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there was another wave coming.\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another wave\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The boat was further out now, but there was still chaos.\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The boat\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3724}, {\"ngram\": \"chaos\", \"from\": 3766, \"to\": 3771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ben Thouard was right there too.\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ben Thouard\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the guy with the broadcast water camera was suddenly gone.\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the guy\", \"from\": 3810, \"to\": 3817}, {\"ngram\": \"the broadcast water camera\", \"from\": 3823, \"to\": 3849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He went over the falls.\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the falls\", \"from\": 3882, \"to\": 3891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I talked to him later and he said he fully hit the reef and was pretty sore.\", \"from\": 3893, \"to\": 3969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 3948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The camera was fine; they just had to fix a few things.\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 4025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The camera\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 3980}, {\"ngram\": \"a few things\", \"from\": 4012, \"to\": 4024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he said he saw the same thing I did.\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same thing\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He saw the propeller underwater.\", \"from\": 4067, \"to\": 4099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the propeller underwater\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those (broadcast) cameras are so buoyant that he just got sucked over when he stopped swimming.\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those (broadcast) cameras\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you swim under a wave, like when you saw the propeller, are you only kicking your flippers or using your free arm too?\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a wave\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4223}, {\"ngram\": \"the propeller\", \"from\": 4243, \"to\": 4256}, {\"ngram\": \"your flippers\", \"from\": 4279, \"to\": 4292}, {\"ngram\": \"your free arm\", \"from\": 4302, \"to\": 4315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It depends.\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's mainly your flippers, but one good stroke with your arm can help too if needed.\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your flippers\", \"from\": 4346, \"to\": 4359}, {\"ngram\": \"one good stroke\", \"from\": 4365, \"to\": 4380}, {\"ngram\": \"your arm\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the wave is sucking and you feel that suction, you can use it in your favor if you go deep and catch that current.\", \"from\": 4419, \"to\": 4538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 4424, \"to\": 4432}, {\"ngram\": \"that suction\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4469}, {\"ngram\": \"your favor\", \"from\": 4489, \"to\": 4499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it was pure luck that you were shooting in the water that day?\", \"from\": 4540, \"to\": 4605, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pure luck\", \"from\": 4550, \"to\": 4559}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 4586, \"to\": 4595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exactly.\", \"from\": 4607, \"to\": 4615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We got our roster for who's shooting water and that day was my turn.\", \"from\": 4616, \"to\": 4684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our roster\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4633}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 4653, \"to\": 4658}, {\"ngram\": \"that day\", \"from\": 4663, \"to\": 4671}, {\"ngram\": \"my turn\", \"from\": 4676, \"to\": 4683}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was supposed to shoot six heats, but I was like, this is too good.\", \"from\": 4685, \"to\": 4753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six heats\", \"from\": 4709, \"to\": 4718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not go in.\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My battery was running out, so I went to the boat to change the batteries.\", \"from\": 4771, \"to\": 4845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My battery\", \"from\": 4771, \"to\": 4781}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 4812, \"to\": 4820}, {\"ngram\": \"the batteries\", \"from\": 4831, \"to\": 4844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I called (the ISA media manager) and told him it was too good.\", \"from\": 4846, \"to\": 4908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ISA media manager\", \"from\": 4856, \"to\": 4877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to stay longer.\", \"from\": 4909, \"to\": 4930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I missed a few good waves when I was in the boat changing batteries, but you can not get it all.\", \"from\": 4931, \"to\": 5027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few good waves\", \"from\": 4940, \"to\": 4956}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4979}, {\"ngram\": \"changing batteries\", \"from\": 4980, \"to\": 4998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Pablo Jime\\u0301nez (@pablojimenez_photo) What's the best shot you got that day?\", \"from\": 5029, \"to\": 5124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A post\", \"from\": 5029, \"to\": 5035}, {\"ngram\": \"Pablo Jime\\u0301nez\", \"from\": 5046, \"to\": 5060}, {\"ngram\": \"@pablojimenez_photo\", \"from\": 5062, \"to\": 5081}, {\"ngram\": \"the best shot\", \"from\": 5090, \"to\": 5103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were some really good moments.\", \"from\": 5126, \"to\": 5162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some really good moments\", \"from\": 5137, \"to\": 5161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I like Kauli Vaast's wave when he's right at the bottom and the lip is over him.\", \"from\": 5163, \"to\": 5243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5176, \"end\": 5181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 5208, \"to\": 5218}, {\"ngram\": \"the lip\", \"from\": 5223, \"to\": 5230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Right at that time of the day, the sky opened up and the light was perfect.\", \"from\": 5244, \"to\": 5319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 5253, \"to\": 5262}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 5266, \"to\": 5273}, {\"ngram\": \"the sky\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5282}, {\"ngram\": \"the light\", \"from\": 5297, \"to\": 5306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are a couple of Alan Cleland around the same time.\", \"from\": 5320, \"to\": 5376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5347, \"end\": 5354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Burton_Cleland\", \"score\": 0.9999968966588263, \"rank\": 3.102438521856295e-06, \"text\": \"Cleland\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Burton_Cleland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Burton_Cleland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 5330, \"to\": 5338}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 5362, \"to\": 5375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then Medina's 9.9, of course.\", \"from\": 5377, \"to\": 5410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5386, \"end\": 5392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.914450265791664e-28, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 5403, \"to\": 5409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where were you for Medina's 9.9?\", \"from\": 5412, \"to\": 5444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was in the perfect spot.\", \"from\": 5446, \"to\": 5472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the perfect spot\", \"from\": 5455, \"to\": 5471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It kind of caught me off guard at the beginning of the heat.\", \"from\": 5473, \"to\": 5533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"guard\", \"from\": 5498, \"to\": 5503}, {\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 5507, \"to\": 5520}, {\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 5524, \"to\": 5532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was a little bit too zoomed out.\", \"from\": 5534, \"to\": 5568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I managed to work it out.\", \"from\": 5569, \"to\": 5598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a previous conversation, you told me therecent near-drowning incidentof another photographer did not cross your mind that day.\", \"from\": 5600, \"to\": 5729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a previous conversation\", \"from\": 5603, \"to\": 5626}, {\"ngram\": \"therecent near-drowning incidentof\", \"from\": 5640, \"to\": 5674}, {\"ngram\": \"another photographer\", \"from\": 5675, \"to\": 5695}, {\"ngram\": \"your mind\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But how did you know you were ready to shoot in such conditions?\", \"from\": 5730, \"to\": 5794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such conditions\", \"from\": 5778, \"to\": 5793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teahupo'o is probably the heaviest, most perfect wave that I have shot.\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heaviest, most perfect wave\", \"from\": 5818, \"to\": 5849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I have been out in the water at Punta de Lobos (Chile) when it was big and scary.\", \"from\": 5868, \"to\": 5953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5920, \"end\": 5925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9999999297697311, \"rank\": 6.999126255637881e-08, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 5891, \"to\": 5900}, {\"ngram\": \"Punta de Lobos\", \"from\": 5904, \"to\": 5918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is this wave in northern Chile called La Cosa (that I have shot).\", \"from\": 5954, \"to\": 6025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5985, \"end\": 5990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9999999297697311, \"rank\": 6.999126255637881e-08, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}, {\"beg